original_title: Ana Popovic Band: An Evening At Trasimeno Lake
overview: A concert of The Ana Popovic Band during their 'Blind For Love' tour. Over 2 hours of music with an enthusiastic 5000+ audicen, an eight-piece band and a top crew with six camera's to witness this unforgattable evening.
title: Ana Popovic Band: An Evening At Trasimeno Lake
